#

Chicken Salad Bowl

25 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

HealthyEasyQuickSalad

Description

A fresh, vibrant bowl of chicken, greens, and veggies tossed in a light dressing, perfect for a quick and healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • cooked chicken breast: 1 cup, shredded
  • mixed greens (spinach, arugula): 2 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1/2 cup, halved
  • cucumber: 1/2, diced
  • avocado: 1/2, sliced
  • feta cheese: 1/4 cup, crumbled
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
